PrecisOrder directing that the financial year of the CANADA POST CORPORATION shall begin on the last Sunday in March (or April 1 if a Sunday) and shall end on the last Saturday prior to April 1 in the following year, beginning in the fiscal year commencing on April 1, 1993.
